snippet.title: Yopaz IceStar for Atari STe
snippet.description:
Yopaz IceStar is a brilliant puzzler by Cedric Bourse, so I bought myself a copy and you can read more here: https://ataricrypt.blogspot.com/2015/11/yopaz-icestar.html
